items.name: UnMarioWiki
items.title: UnMarioWiki
items.headline: Welcome to the UnMario Wiki
items.desc: Welcome to the UnMario Wiki! This wiki is dedicated to "shaming" the Mario franchise! Hate Mario? Feel free to join other fans in providing reasons for your dislike of Mario and chat with a community that has similar interests! The UnMario Wiki has articles about characters, merchandise, and more! Enter now to learn more!

items.name: MarioWiki
items.title: MarioWiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Mario Wiki
items.desc: MarioWiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to the Mario series. Featuring over 6,000 articles and growing since the wiki's formation on July 2007. The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit any article, so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for the Mario series.

items.name: Super Mario Wiki
items.title: Super Mario Wiki
items.headline: Super Mario Wiki
items.desc: Super Mario Wiki es la enciclopedia en español dedicada al personaje estrella de la compañía Nintendo, Mario. El proyecto recopila toda la información relacionada con el popular personaje; incluyendo todos los videojuegos donde participa; con sagas propias como Mario Bros y otras como Super Smash o Donkey Kong.

items.name: MarioWiki
items.title: MarioWiki
items.headline: MarioWiki - die deutsche Enzyklopädie über das Mario-Universum
items.desc: Das MarioWiki ist eine Enzyklopädie rund um alle Themen der äußerst berühmten, von Nintendo produzierten Mario-Serie, mit den wohl populärsten Videospielcharakteren aller Zeiten in der Hauptrolle. Unser Ziel ist es möglichst viele Informationen über diese Spielserie und all jenes damit in Verbindung stehende zu sammeln, so ist über Spiele, Konsolen, Charaktere, Gegner, Orte, Gegenstände, Angriffe, TV-Serien, Comics und vieles, vieles mehr hinweg, alles in diesem Wiki vertreten. Natürlich werden auch alle Themen der in der Mario-Serie entstandenen Donkey Kong-, Yoshi- und Wario-Serie behandelt. Gegründet wurde das MarioWiki im Jahr 2007 und verfügt seitdem bereits über mehr als 4000 Artikel und 9000 Mediendateien.Wir freuen uns natürlich über jeden, der uns bei unserem Projekt hilft!

items.name: Mario Kart Racing Wiki
items.title: Mario Kart Racing Wiki
items.headline: Avoid the bananas, visit the Mario Kart Wiki
items.desc:
We are creating the gamers' guide to Mario Kart, and you can help!

Mario Kart is a series of racing video games published by Nintendo, featuring a number of characters from the company's "Mario" license. The object is to traverse various racetracks using a character's vehicle of the player's choice, using a variety of Items to assist oneself, in order to be the first competitor to cross the finish line.

items.name: Paper Mario Wiki
items.title: Paper Mario Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Paper Mario Wiki!
items.desc: The Paper Mario wiki is dedicated to the Paper Mario series of Role-Playing games created by Nintendo. The Paper Mario series is set in the Mario universe. The series debuted in 2001 with the release of Paper Mario for the Nintendo 64. Please join our wiki and feel free to contribute articles and edit the wiki!

items.name: Super Mario Fanon
items.title: Super Mario Fanon
items.headline: Welcome to Mario Fanon Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Mario Fanon Wikia! The Mario Fanon Wikia is a Super Mario fanfiction wiki that anyone can edit. This site encourages fans of Mario to write anything, literally anything fictional, on Mario and his spin-offs, affiliates, friends, colleagues, villains, rooms, places, countries, leaders, species, etc.! Enter now to see what's on the site and how you can contribute!

items.name: マリオペディア
items.title: マリオペディア
items.headline: マリオの百科事典、マリオペディアへようこそ！
items.desc:
誰もが知っている『マリオ』とは、主に任天堂から発売されているゲームのマリオシリーズ、およびメディアミックスに登場するキャラクター。シリーズとしては最古の一つである。このコミュニティーでは『マリオ』が登場するゲームに出てくる敵、仲間、アイテムなどの記事が満載。

このコミュニティーで下記のことをすることができます。 
1、情報を編集することができます。
2、情報を提供することができます。
3、仲間を見つけてフォーラムで話したりすることが可能です。

編集作業を行う場合はぜひぜひ、アカウントを登録してログインして下さい。
また、このコミュニティーでは管理者を募集しています。我こそはと思われる方はご連絡下さい。

items.name: Mario Kart Wii Wiki
items.title: Mario Kart Wii Wiki
items.desc: Mario Kart Wii Wiki is a database for information on Mario Kart Wii, and the whole Mario franchise! It also has several unique features, like User Reviews, Comparisons, and Top Tens, and several helpful admins!

items.name: Super Mario Bros. Z Wiki
items.title: Super Mario Bros. Z Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Super Mario Bros. Z wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to the Super Mario Bros. Z wiki! Super Mario Bros. Z (SMBZ) is a Flash animation series created by Alvin-Earthworm. The series first debuted on April 22, 2006 at the popular flash site Newgrounds. It is a crossover between the Mario and Sonic franchises, and draws heavy influence from the Dragon Ball franchise, such as the choreography of the fighting scenes, powering up, and free flight. The series has reached well known popularity over the 2006 year and continues onward during 2012. The series was and still is famous for its "Outstanding Achievement in a Fan-made web-series". The series is targeted for 13 year olds and up only due to the promoted violence and mild language.

items.name: Stupid Mario Brothers Wiki
items.title: Stupid Mario Brothers Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Stupid Super Mario Brothers Wiki!
items.desc: Stupid Mario Brothers (shortened as Stupid Mario Bros. or simply abbreviated as SMB) is an Internet-based web series Live-Action on YouTube, created by Richard Michael Alvarez. It tells the story of the show's main characters Mario, Luigi, Wario, and Waluigi and their wild adventures in the Real World. Along the way, they meet a variety of allies and enemies that all play their part in changing the Real World as they know it. The first episode aired on December 29, 2007, with great success. The show ended on June 5, 2012, with the conclusion of Season Five.

items.headline: Il suffit de sauter pour contribuer !
items.desc: Le Wiki Mario, c'est une encyclopédie en ligne francophone comprenant 4 610 articles dédiés à Mario et à son univers et ouverte à tous les utilisateurs connectés depuis 2009 ! Découvrez le monde du plombier moustachu sous un angle inédit, partagez vos connaissances avec les autres utilisateurs, contribuez vous-même en modifiant ou en créant des articles, ajoutez des images à votre guise... Bref, sur le Wiki Mario comme au Royaume Champignon, les possibilités sont infinies !

items.name: Newer Super Mario Bros. Wiki
items.title: Newer Super Mario Bros. Wiki
items.headline: Newer Super Mario Bros. Wii Wiki
items.desc:
The above is a forum for those of us who would like to unite (using soon-to-be-released level editor Reggie!) in helping to create (to completion!) a full-on sequel game to New Super Mario Bros. Wii, that is, something that is not a 1:1 remake of a past Mario/other game, and not an experimental hack, but more so a richly detailed, well crafted, fully featured (if eventually possible) series of levels (and perhaps world maps, as well) that could rival the quality of the original NSMBW game, which is, of course, of an INCREDIBLY high standard.

So this is something that will require time, patience, and a lot of planning and community spirit, and also a bit of modesty in case some levels you make or some of your ideas prove unpopular or unsuccessful or whatever. I recommend all of those who are enthusiastic about adhering to these general "sequel" principles to join!
